  <span id="freeText934559213808547560" style="display:none">Alisa Mullen is a favourite of mine and I was looking forward to reading her newest release, especially after hearing such great reviews on social media. I am in agreement on the whole with those positive reviews. Nate is a hottie there is no doubt about that, however there is something missing from his personality to put him high up my book boyfriend list. He is just not alpha male enough for me. Sunny is a girl broken from a life full of misunderstanding. Nate brings the sun back into her life. The topic of addiction is prevalent throughout and is realistically portrayed and not dramatized. Overall I enjoyed this book and award it 4 stars ~ Rosie</span>
