<div id="review_1199277442" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1199277442" />
    <a title="Misha Estrada" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/19198843-misha-estrada"><img alt="Misha Estrada" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1365380263p2/19198843.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1199277442?book_show_action=true">Feb 12, 2015</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Misha Estrada" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Misha Estrada" href="/user/show/19198843-misha-estrada">Misha Estrada</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/24882614-following-the-sun">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/19198843-misha-estrada?shelf=romance">romance</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/19198843-misha-estrada?shelf=contemporary">contemporary</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1199277442" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6815495926638627073">I loved this story. It had great characters, very believable. I loved Sunny, which surprised me. I imagine it is pretty difficult to write a drug addict into a likable character. (I know drug addicts, and while I love them, they are difficult to like a lot of the time.) I liked that the story is hopeful, but not an unrealistic fairy tale. It&apos;s a great piece of writing. Very real.</span>
  <span id="freeText6815495926638627073" style="display:none">I loved this story. It had great characters, very believable. I loved Sunny, which surprised me. I imagine it is pretty difficult to write a drug addict into a likable character. (I know drug addicts, and while I love them, they are difficult to like a lot of the time.) I liked that the story is hopeful, but not an unrealistic fairy tale. It's a great piece of writing. Very real.</span>
  <a data-text-id="6815495926638627073" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
