<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer10916661372786332335">Alisa Mullen is the author of the Best Selling Saga, The Chosen Series and the Best Selling psychological suspense novels, Plastic Confidence and Artificial Love. She also published Following the Sun,77 Steps, One Missing Link,The Business Trip, and many other short stories and novellas. She has resurfaced in 2019 to finish The Good Bye Trilogy. <br/><br/>Even though Alisa grew up in Down East Maine, she re</span>
  <span id="freeText10916661372786332335" style="display:none">Alisa Mullen is the author of the Best Selling Saga, The Chosen Series and the Best Selling psychological suspense novels, Plastic Confidence and Artificial Love. She also published Following the Sun,77 Steps, One Missing Link,The Business Trip, and many other short stories and novellas. She has resurfaced in 2019 to finish The Good Bye Trilogy. <br /><br />Even though Alisa grew up in Down East Maine, she received a BA from Texas A&amp;M University and a MS from Our Lady of Lake University in San Antonio, Texas. When she isn't writing, she enjoys hiking the Texas Hill Country, traveling and cultivating her other talents. <br /><br />Mullen lives in Schertz, Texas with her two teens and their animals. Please email her at alimullenbooks@gmail.com</span>
  <a data-text-id="10916661372786332335" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

